[{"title":"Hello World","url":"/2022/07/02/hello-world/","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight open bash\"><span class=\"code-header\">    <span class=\"code-title\">      <div class=\"code-icon\"></div>BASH 共 1 行</span>      <span class=\"code-header-tail\">        <button class=\"code-copy\"></button>        <span class=\"code-space\">展开</span></span></span></span>    <div class=\"code-box\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">$ hexo new <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight open bash\"><span class=\"code-header\">    <span class=\"code-title\">      <div class=\"code-icon\"></div>BASH 共 1 行</span>      <span class=\"code-header-tail\">        <button class=\"code-copy\"></button>        <span class=\"code-space\">展开</span></span></span></span>    <div class=\"code-box\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">$ hexo server<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight open bash\"><span class=\"code-header\">    <span class=\"code-title\">      <div class=\"code-icon\"></div>BASH 共 1 行</span>      <span class=\"code-header-tail\">        <button class=\"code-copy\"></button>        <span class=\"code-space\">展开</span></span></span></span>    <div class=\"code-box\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">$ hexo generate<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight open bash\"><span class=\"code-header\">    <span class=\"code-title\">      <div class=\"code-icon\"></div>BASH 共 1 行</span>      <span class=\"code-header-tail\">        <button class=\"code-copy\"></button>        <span class=\"code-space\">展开</span></span></span></span>    <div class=\"code-box\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">$ hexo deploy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\">Deployment</a></p>\n"},{"title":"测试","url":"/2022/07/02/%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/","content":"<p>博客这样算是成功建起来了，目前还没能够学会如何自定义博客排版，hexo 以及 markdown 都属于完全不会只会照搬的系列，github 指令不是很熟更新会比较慢，欢迎交流。也欢迎来找我摆烂摸鱼 (BUSHI)。<br>这里尝试上传张艾莉妮的图片：<br><img src=\"/image/Irene.jpg\" alt=\"我的心会做出判决！\"><br>个人目标： 在摆烂的道路上越走越远。更加高效地摆烂。</p>\n","categories":["takedown"],"tags":["test"]}]